<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Appointment Letter</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #000;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px;
            background: white;
            font-size: 12pt;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #000;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .company-name {
            font-size: 20pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #000;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .company-address {
            font-size: 11pt;
            color: #000;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .document-title {
            font-size: 16pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
            color: #000;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .date-ref {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 11pt;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: justify;
        }
        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .details-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 2px solid #000;
        }
        .details-table th,
        .details-table td {
            border: 1px solid #000;
            padding: 12px;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 11pt;
        }
        .details-table th {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 50px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .signature-box {
            text-align: center;
            width: 45%;
        }
        .signature-line {
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
            margin-top: 60px;
            padding-top: 5px;
            font-size: 11pt;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: #666;
            border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }
        .terms-section {
            margin: 25px 0;
            border: 1px solid #000;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .terms-title {
            font-size: 12pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .terms-list {
            list-style: decimal;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .terms-list li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 11pt;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="company-name">{{companyName}}</div>
        <div class="company-address">{{companyAddress}}</div>
        {{#if companyPhone}}<div>Phone: {{companyPhone}} {{#if companyEmail}}| Email: {{companyEmail}}{{/if}}</div>{{/if}}
    </div>

    <div class="document-title">Appointment Letter</div>

    <div class="date-ref">
        <div><strong>Date:</strong> {{appointmentDate}}</div>
        {{#if refNumber}}<div><strong>Ref:</strong> {{refNumber}}</div>{{/if}}
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p><strong>To,</strong></p>
        <p><strong>{{employeeName}}</strong><br>
        {{#if employeeAddress}}{{employeeAddress}}{{/if}}</p>

        <p><strong>Subject: Appointment as {{position}}</strong></p>

        <p>Dear {{employeeName}},</p>

        <p>We are pleased to inform you that you have been appointed as <strong>{{position}}</strong> in the <strong>{{department}}</strong> department of {{companyName}}, effective from <strong>{{startDate}}</strong>.</p>

        <p>Your appointment is subject to the terms and conditions mentioned below and as per the company policies:</p>

        <table class="details-table">
            <tr>
                <th>Employee Name</th>
                <td>{{employeeName}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Position</th>
                <td>{{position}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Department</th>
                <td>{{department}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Date of Appointment</th>
                <td>{{appointmentDate}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Reporting Manager</th>
                <td>{{reportingTo}}</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Work Location</th>
                <td>{{workLocation}}</td>
            </tr>
            {{#if probationPeriod}}
            <tr>
                <th>Probation Period</th>
                <td>{{probationPeriod}}</td>
            </tr>
            {{/if}}
        </table>

        <div class="terms-section">
            <div class="terms-title">Terms and Conditions</div>
            <ol class="terms-list">
                <li>You will be governed by the rules, regulations, and policies of the company as amended from time to time.</li>
                <li>You are required to maintain confidentiality of all company information and data.</li>
                <li>Your employment is subject to satisfactory completion of probation period{{#if probationPeriod}} of {{probationPeriod}}{{/if}}.</li>
                <li>You will be required to give {{#if noticePeriod}}{{noticePeriod}}{{else}}30 days{{/if}} notice in writing before leaving the organization.</li>
                <li>The company reserves the right to terminate your services with appropriate notice as per company policy.</li>
                <li>You will be entitled to benefits as per company policy including health insurance and paid leave.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <p>We welcome you to our organization and look forward to a long and mutually beneficial association.</p>

        <p>Please confirm your acceptance of this appointment by signing and returning a copy of this letter.</p>

        <p>Congratulations and welcome to {{companyName}}!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="signature-box">
            <div class="signature-line">
                <strong>For {{companyName}}</strong><br>
                {{#if hrContactPerson}}{{hrContactPerson}}{{else}}HR Manager{{/if}}<br>
                Human Resources
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="signature-box">
            <div class="signature-line">
                <strong>Employee Acceptance</strong><br>
                {{employeeName}}<br>
                Date: ___________
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is a computer-generated document and does not require a physical signature.</p>
        <p>{{companyName}} - Professional Document System</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>